wad-simulator-js is a browser JavaScript PORT of the WAD/UCFX/sges format layer
of the Mercenaries-Fan-Build "mercs2-wad-simulator" project, which is itself
MIT-licensed. The file formats, the reference implementation (`mercs2_formats`)
and all the reverse-engineering behind them are that project's work; this
repository only re-expresses their read/write logic in JavaScript so it can run
in a browser, and adds a front end. See CREDITS.md and the README.

